-- Toyota to Cut Production Plan in North America by 10%, Nikkan Kogyo Says
-- B y   K a z u y o   S a w a
-- 2010-10-05T22:21:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/toyota-to-cut-production-plan-in-north-america-by-10-nikkan-kogyo-says.html
Toyota Motor Corp. will cut
production in North America by 10 percent from an earlier plan
during the three-month period through December, the Nikkan Kogyo
newspaper reported, citing an unidentified company executive.   The automaker will reduce output by about 40,000 vehicles
mainly at its Kentucky plant, the report said.    To contact the reporter on this story:
